    <section class="description">
     <div class="description__text description__text--rich">
      <section class="show-more-less-html" data-max-lines="5">
       <div class="show-more-less-html__markup show-more-less-html__markup--clamp-after-5">
        <p>For one of our clients we are currently recruiting a<strong> Java Software Developer (m/w/d)&nbsp;</strong>to join their team in Barcelona.</p>
        <p><br></p>
        <p>My client is an international&nbsp;<strong>media company</strong>, that&nbsp;<strong>connects</strong>&nbsp;Advertisers, Agencies, Brands &amp; Developers.&nbsp;The team is culturally diverse and consists of tech lovers and goal achievers, constantly creating new ways of connection with the outside world. They are working with a holistic approach towards buying and analyzing media, while<strong> using real-time data </strong>to generate <strong>data mining</strong>, allowing them to visualize trends to acquire and engage users. </p>
        <p><br></p>
        <p>They are a group of believers, believing in their mission which is to build a greater and more connected tomorrow!</p>
        <p><br></p>
        <p>The person that also shares this dream and helps them achieve this mission will bring:</p>
        <ul>
         <li>3-4 years of experience as a Java Developer.</li>
         <li>Solid knowledge in Kafka and Redis.</li>
         <li>Deep understanding of Web Technologies.</li>
         <li>Familiar with Methodologies: Agile, Scrum.</li>
         <li>Ability and willingness to learn new languages and technologies.</li>
         <li>Understanding of how to build modular and scalable solution architecture.</li>
         <li>Ability Integrating multiple technologies and data sources Design and implementation of microservices.</li>
         <li>Business fluency in English, Spanish is a plus.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Nice to have:</p>
        <ul>
         <li>Knowledge in Apache Ignite, Elastic search, Python, Go, Jetty, Docker, Git, Apache Druid, MySQL, Angular, Django</li>
        </ul>
        <p><br></p>
        <p>Besides enormous growth opportunities you will join a global team with a fun work atmosphere.</p>
        <p>If you want to learn more I am looking forward to receive your English CV and telling you about this exciting opportunity!</p>
        <p><br></p>
        <p>Apply on Linkedin or write me on sarah.stade@talentedint.com</p>
       </div><button class="show-more-less-html__button show-more-less-html__button--more" data-tracking-control-name="public_jobs_show-more-html-btn" aria-label="Mostrar m√°s" aria-expanded="false">Mostrar m√°s
        <icon class="show-more-less-html__button-icon" data-delayed-url="https://static-exp1.licdn.com/sc/h/cyolgscd0imw2ldqppkrb84vo" /></button><button class="show-more-less-html__button show-more-less-html__button--less" data-tracking-control-name="public_jobs_show-less-html-btn" aria-label="Mostrar menos" aria-expanded="true">Mostrar menos
        <icon class="show-more-less-html__button-icon" data-delayed-url="https://static-exp1.licdn.com/sc/h/4chtt12k98xwnba1nimld2oyg" /></button>

    <section class="description">
     <div class="description__text description__text--rich">
      <section class="show-more-less-html" data-max-lines="5">
       <div class="show-more-less-html__markup show-more-less-html__markup--clamp-after-5">
        <p>For one of our clients we are currently recruiting a<strong> Java Software Developer (m/w/d)&nbsp;</strong>to join their team in Barcelona.</p>
        <p><br></p>
        <p>My client is an international&nbsp;<strong>media company</strong>, that&nbsp;<strong>connects</strong>&nbsp;Advertisers, Agencies, Brands &amp; Developers.&nbsp;The team is culturally diverse and consists of tech lovers and goal achievers, constantly creating new ways of connection with the outside world. They are working with a holistic approach towards buying and analyzing media, while<strong> using real-time data </strong>to generate <strong>data mining</strong>, allowing them to visualize trends to acquire and engage users. </p>
        <p><br></p>
        <p>They are a group of believers, believing in their mission which is to build a greater and more connected tomorrow!</p>
        <p><br></p>
        <p>The person that also shares this dream and helps them achieve this mission will bring:</p>
        <ul>
         <li>3-4 years of experience as a Java Developer.</li>
         <li>Solid knowledge in Kafka and Redis.</li>
         <li>Deep understanding of Web Technologies.</li>
         <li>Familiar with Methodologies: Agile, Scrum.</li>
         <li>Ability and willingness to learn new languages and technologies.</li>
         <li>Understanding of how to build modular and scalable solution architecture.</li>
         <li>Ability Integrating multiple technologies and data sources Design and implementation of microservices.</li>
         <li>Business fluency in English, Spanish is a plus.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Nice to have:</p>
        <ul>
         <li>Knowledge in Apache Ignite, Elastic search, Python, Go, Jetty, Docker, Git, Apache Druid, MySQL, Angular, Django</li>
        </ul>
        <p><br></p>
        <p>Besides enormous growth opportunities you will join a global team with a fun work atmosphere.</p>
        <p>If you want to learn more I am looking forward to receive your English CV and telling you about this exciting opportunity!</p>
        <p><br></p>
        <p>Apply on Linkedin or write me on sarah.stade@talentedint.com</p>
       </div><button class="show-more-less-html__button show-more-less-html__button--more" data-tracking-control-name="public_jobs_show-more-html-btn" aria-label="Mostrar m√°s" aria-expanded="false">Mostrar m√°s
        <icon class="show-more-less-html__button-icon" data-delayed-url="https://static-exp1.licdn.com/sc/h/cyolgscd0imw2ldqppkrb84vo" /></button><button class="show-more-less-html__button show-more-less-html__button--less" data-tracking-control-name="public_jobs_show-less-html-btn" aria-label="Mostrar menos" aria-expanded="true">Mostrar menos
        <icon class="show-more-less-html__button-icon" data-delayed-url="https://static-exp1.licdn.com/sc/h/4chtt12k98xwnba1nimld2oyg" /></button>

   <section class="description">
    <div class="description__text description__text--rich">
     <section class="show-more-less-html" data-max-lines="5">
      <div class="show-more-less-html__markup show-more-less-html__markup--clamp-after-5">
       <p>For one of our clients we are currently recruiting a<strong> Java Software Developer (m/w/d)&nbsp;</strong>to join their team in Barcelona.</p>
       <p><br></p>
       <p>My client is an international&nbsp;<strong>media company</strong>, that&nbsp;<strong>connects</strong>&nbsp;Advertisers, Agencies, Brands &amp; Developers.&nbsp;The team is culturally diverse and consists of tech lovers and goal achievers, constantly creating new ways of connection with the outside world. They are working with a holistic approach towards buying and analyzing media, while<strong> using real-time data </strong>to generate <strong>data mining</strong>, allowing them to visualize trends to acquire and engage users. </p>
       <p><br></p>
       <p>They are a group of believers, believing in their mission which is to build a greater and more connected tomorrow!</p>
       <p><br></p>
       <p>The person that also shares this dream and helps them achieve this mission will bring:</p>
       <ul>
        <li>3-4 years of experience as a Java Developer.</li>
        <li>Solid knowledge in Kafka and Redis.</li>
        <li>Deep understanding of Web Technologies.</li>
        <li>Familiar with Methodologies: Agile, Scrum.</li>
        <li>Ability and willingness to learn new languages and technologies.</li>
        <li>Understanding of how to build modular and scalable solution architecture.</li>
        <li>Ability Integrating multiple technologies and data sources Design and implementation of microservices.</li>
        <li>Business fluency in English, Spanish is a plus.</li>
       </ul>
       <p>Nice to have:</p>
       <ul>
        <li>Knowledge in Apache Ignite, Elastic search, Python, Go, Jetty, Docker, Git, Apache Druid, MySQL, Angular, Django</li>
       </ul>
       <p><br></p>
       <p>Besides enormous growth opportunities you will join a global team with a fun work atmosphere.</p>
       <p>If you want to learn more I am looking forward to receive your English CV and telling you about this exciting opportunity!</p>
       <p><br></p>
       <p>Apply on Linkedin or write me on sarah.stade@talentedint.com</p>

       <icon class="show-more-less-html__button-icon" data-delayed-url="https://static-exp1.licdn.com/sc/h/cyolgscd0imw2ldqppkrb84vo" /></button><button class="show-more-less-html__button show-more-less-html__button--less" data-tracking-control-name="public_jobs_show-less-html-btn" aria-label="Mostrar menos" aria-expanded="true">Mostrar menos
       <icon class="show-more-less-html__button-icon" data-delayed-url="https://static-exp1.licdn.com/sc/h/4chtt12k98xwnba1nimld2oyg" /></button>

  <section class="description">
   <div class="description__text description__text--rich">
    <section class="show-more-less-html" data-max-lines="5">
     <div class="show-more-less-html__markup show-more-less-html__markup--clamp-after-5">
      <p>For one of our clients we are currently recruiting a<strong> Java Software Developer (m/w/d)&nbsp;</strong>to join their team in Barcelona.</p>
      <p><br></p>
      <p>My client is an international&nbsp;<strong>media company</strong>, that&nbsp;<strong>connects</strong>&nbsp;Advertisers, Agencies, Brands &amp; Developers.&nbsp;The team is culturally diverse and consists of tech lovers and goal achievers, constantly creating new ways of connection with the outside world. They are working with a holistic approach towards buying and analyzing media, while<strong> using real-time data </strong>to generate <strong>data mining</strong>, allowing them to visualize trends to acquire and engage users. </p>
      <p><br></p>
      <p>They are a group of believers, believing in their mission which is to build a greater and more connected tomorrow!</p>
      <p><br></p>
      <p>The person that also shares this dream and helps them achieve this mission will bring:</p>
      <ul>
       <li>3-4 years of experience as a Java Developer.</li>
       <li>Solid knowledge in Kafka and Redis.</li>
       <li>Deep understanding of Web Technologies.</li>
       <li>Familiar with Methodologies: Agile, Scrum.</li>
       <li>Ability and willingness to learn new languages and technologies.</li>
       <li>Understanding of how to build modular and scalable solution architecture.</li>
       <li>Ability Integrating multiple technologies and data sources Design and implementation of microservices.</li>
       <li>Business fluency in English, Spanish is a plus.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Nice to have:</p>
      <ul>
       <li>Knowledge in Apache Ignite, Elastic search, Python, Go, Jetty, Docker, Git, Apache Druid, MySQL, Angular, Django</li>
      </ul>
      <p><br></p>
      <p>Besides enormous growth opportunities you will join a global team with a fun work atmosphere.</p>
      <p>If you want to learn more I am looking forward to receive your English CV and telling you about this exciting opportunity!</p>
      <p><br></p>
      <p>Apply on Linkedin or write me on sarah.stade@talentedint.com</p>

      <icon class="show-more-less-html__button-icon" data-delayed-url="https://static-exp1.licdn.com/sc/h/cyolgscd0imw2ldqppkrb84vo" /></button><button class="show-more-less-html__button show-more-less-html__button--less" data-tracking-control-name="public_jobs_show-less-html-btn" aria-label="Mostrar menos" aria-expanded="true">Mostrar menos
      <icon class="show-more-less-html__button-icon" data-delayed-url="https://static-exp1.licdn.com/sc/h/4chtt12k98xwnba1nimld2oyg" /></button>

 <section class="description">
  <div class="description__text description__text--rich">
   <section class="show-more-less-html" data-max-lines="5">
    <div class="show-more-less-html__markup show-more-less-html__markup--clamp-after-5">
     <p>For one of our clients we are currently recruiting a<strong> Java Software Developer (m/w/d)&nbsp;</strong>to join their team in Barcelona.</p>
     <p><br></p>
     <p>My client is an international&nbsp;<strong>media company</strong>, that&nbsp;<strong>connects</strong>&nbsp;Advertisers, Agencies, Brands &amp; Developers.&nbsp;The team is culturally diverse and consists of tech lovers and goal achievers, constantly creating new ways of connection with the outside world. They are working with a holistic approach towards buying and analyzing media, while<strong> using real-time data </strong>to generate <strong>data mining</strong>, allowing them to visualize trends to acquire and engage users. </p>
     <p><br></p>
     <p>They are a group of believers, believing in their mission which is to build a greater and more connected tomorrow!</p>
     <p><br></p>
     <p>The person that also shares this dream and helps them achieve this mission will bring:</p>
     <ul>
      <li>3-4 years of experience as a Java Developer.</li>
      <li>Solid knowledge in Kafka and Redis.</li>
      <li>Deep understanding of Web Technologies.</li>
      <li>Familiar with Methodologies: Agile, Scrum.</li>
      <li>Ability and willingness to learn new languages and technologies.</li>
      <li>Understanding of how to build modular and scalable solution architecture.</li>
      <li>Ability Integrating multiple technologies and data sources Design and implementation of microservices.</li>
      <li>Business fluency in English, Spanish is a plus.</li>
     </ul>
     <p>Nice to have:</p>
     <ul>
      <li>Knowledge in Apache Ignite, Elastic search, Python, Go, Jetty, Docker, Git, Apache Druid, MySQL, Angular, Django</li>
     </ul>
     <p><br></p>
     <p>Besides enormous growth opportunities you will join a global team with a fun work atmosphere.</p>
     <p>If you want to learn more I am looking forward to receive your English CV and telling you about this exciting opportunity!</p>
     <p><br></p>
     <p>Apply on Linkedin or write me on sarah.stade@talentedint.com</p>

<section class="description">
 <div class="description__text description__text--rich">
  <section class="show-more-less-html" data-max-lines="5">
   <div class="show-more-less-html__markup show-more-less-html__markup--clamp-after-5">
    <p>For one of our clients we are currently recruiting a<strong> Java Software Developer (m/w/d)&nbsp;</strong>to join their team in Barcelona.</p>
    <p><br></p>
    <p>My client is an international&nbsp;<strong>media company</strong>, that&nbsp;<strong>connects</strong>&nbsp;Advertisers, Agencies, Brands &amp; Developers.&nbsp;The team is culturally diverse and consists of tech lovers and goal achievers, constantly creating new ways of connection with the outside world. They are working with a holistic approach towards buying and analyzing media, while<strong> using real-time data </strong>to generate <strong>data mining</strong>, allowing them to visualize trends to acquire and engage users. </p>
    <p><br></p>
    <p>They are a group of believers, believing in their mission which is to build a greater and more connected tomorrow!</p>
    <p><br></p>
    <p>The person that also shares this dream and helps them achieve this mission will bring:</p>
    <ul>
     <li>3-4 years of experience as a Java Developer.</li>
     <li>Solid knowledge in Kafka and Redis.</li>
     <li>Deep understanding of Web Technologies.</li>
     <li>Familiar with Methodologies: Agile, Scrum.</li>
     <li>Ability and willingness to learn new languages and technologies.</li>
     <li>Understanding of how to build modular and scalable solution architecture.</li>
     <li>Ability Integrating multiple technologies and data sources Design and implementation of microservices.</li>
     <li>Business fluency in English, Spanish is a plus.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Nice to have:</p>
    <ul>
     <li>Knowledge in Apache Ignite, Elastic search, Python, Go, Jetty, Docker, Git, Apache Druid, MySQL, Angular, Django</li>
    </ul>
    <p><br></p>
    <p>Besides enormous growth opportunities you will join a global team with a fun work atmosphere.</p>
    <p>If you want to learn more I am looking forward to receive your English CV and telling you about this exciting opportunity!</p>
    <p><br></p>
    <p>Apply on Linkedin or write me on sarah.stade@talentedint.com</p>
